HEADWORD: Altaic
<hw>Al*ta"ic</hw></mhw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>alta⟦ium⟧que</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to the Altai, a
mountain chain in Central Asia.</def>⟦br⟧
