==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Altaic
<hw>Altaic</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a collective term for a group of
related linguistic families including the Turkic, Tungusik and Mongolian
languages, spoken over a broad area from southeastern Europe and Asia,
as far east as the Pacific.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Altaic</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Altaic
<hw>Altaic</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>of or pertaining to the
Altaic languages.</def> <illu><ex>Altaic</ex> languages</illu>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

